
-- Using the Docker image:

$ docker build -t proxy nginx/
$ docker run -p 80:80 proxy


-- Using the command line tool:

$ python 3scale.py -h
usage: 3scale.py [-h] [-u HTTP_USER] [-p HTTP_PASSWD] [proxy]

positional arguments:
  proxy                 proxy server

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -u HTTP_USER, --http_user HTTP_USER
                        HTTP user name
  -p HTTP_PASSWD, --http_passwd HTTP_PASSWD
                        HTTP password


-- HTTP authentication (nginx/conf/htpasswd): user "3scale", password "3scale"